{"tid":1385620,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實對班狗唔係硬拼，而係識玩游擊","createTime":"2019-07-30T06:26:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T09:33:14.000Z","uid":104004,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8131026c1aeb2a37320009098220e481e640e65f","tid":1385620,"uid":104004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:26:44.000Z","msg":"同班狗打陣地戰<br />\n對班勇武黎講係好刺激<br />\n但好損兵節將<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真正令班狗潰散<br />\n係要善用游擊戰術<br />\n<br />\n簡單啲講，每次示威，同一時間，超過1個地點以上<br />\n(類似721元朗西環咁)<br />\n班狗唔能夠同時兼顧2邊以上戰線<br />\n人手編排同調動難度會大增<br />\n<br />\n而勇武既職責就係保護示威者不受促龍突襲，保住防線，全身而退，狗退我進，狗進我退，令佢疲於奔命撲個空，人又捉唔到，假又請唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n長玩落去，狗隊必定崩潰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"875987c6150f6c3bdea80eb87475a8ca531fda46","tid":1385620,"uid":293257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:31:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de5db57bbab0422cace7ae60df81702ffc6a60a3","tid":1385620,"uid":164938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:32:16.000Z","msg":"Fact checked<br />\n明天機場博覽館要人！！<br />\n7.31<br />\n16:00-17:30<br />\n機場Asia World Expo-Summit 2號展館<br />\n政府開pre policy address meeting! <br />\n會議是為運輸及貿易界而設既諮詢會，將有好多公司出席！<br />\n<br />\n聽日7.31機場博覽館要人！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1385635\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1385635</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ebf15d84cfaa57d414feb088527448112a0e6a91","tid":1385620,"uid":104004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"875987c6150f6c3bdea80eb87475a8ca531fda46","tid":1385620,"uid":293257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:31:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"cit